Hwaet. We Gardena in geardagum, 
beodcyninga, brym gefrunon, 
hu oa aebelingas ellen fremedon. 
Oft Scyld Scefing sceabena breatum, 
monegum maegbum, meodosetla ofteah, 
egsode eorlas. Syooan aerest wearo 
feasceaft funden, he baes frofre gebad, 
weox under wolcnum, weoromyndum bah, 
oobaet him aeghwylc bara ymbsittendra 
ofer hronrade hyran scolde, 
gomban gyldan. baet waes god cyning. 
oaem eafera waes aefter cenned, 
geong in geardum, bone god sende 
folce to frofre; fyrenoearfe ongeat 
be hie aer drugon aldorlease 
lange hwile. Him baes liffrea, 
wuldres wealdend, woroldare forgeaf; 
Beowulf waes breme blaed wide sprang, 
Scyldes eafera Scedelandum in. 